## External integration documentation (optional)

When this project integrates with **vendor-published APIs, XSDs, PDFs, or OpenAPI/HTML specs**, cache reference artifacts under **`.ai/docs/integration/`**.

Rules:

1. **Subfolders:** Organize by source and version (e.g. `.ai/docs/integration/vendor-v1/`) so upgrades do not silently overwrite pinned files.
2. **Manifest:** Record every download in `.ai/docs/integration/MANIFEST.txt` (source URL, local path, batch date).
3. **Sources:** Prefer official vendor domains; third-party mirrors only with an explicit manifest note.
4. **Secrets:** Never place keys, PEM/P12, passwords, tokens, or `.env` content in this directory.
5. **Verification:** After download, confirm file type (not an HTML error page masquerading as a PDF).
6. **Scope:** Vendor artifacts only — not customer exports or operational uploads.

Prefer reading **cached copies** during implementation; refresh when vendor versions change.

